{"title":"遗孤——雨花台抒情","authors":["黄东成"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":4,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"遗孤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——雨花台抒情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄东成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"临刑前的母亲，抱起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"襁褓中的婴孩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奶头塞进花瓣似的小嘴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最后喂一口伟大的母爱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"婴儿贪婪地吮吸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吮着奶——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奶水渗着血块，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带血的刺刀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将婴儿，从母亲心上撕开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遗嘱是布条上一行血字："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——孩子，记住，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是革命的后代！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪声中，母亲英勇殉难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命，哺育出共和国崭新时代。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似一棵长在岩缝的小树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子在共和国的阳光下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茁壮成长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许今天他已是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚手架上的建筑工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"研究宇宙天体的学者……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幼小的心灵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信念早熟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽记不清母亲的慈容，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却永远忘不了伟大的母爱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献身于母亲为之献身的事业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追求母亲所追求的光辉未来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不渝的坚贞，一代代前仆后继。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，崛起的一代新人，布条上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血写的遗嘱已溶进血脉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨花台跳动着母亲的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谆谆叮嘱：莫忘重任在肩。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}